  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators set out to evaluate the effects of the traditional Chinese medicinal
      mixture under the brand name YangXinShi (YXS) on the prognosis in patients with chronic heart
      failure when it is combined with the optimal combination drug treatment of heart failure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
